column5: I'm always kinda shy til someone breaks the ice.
ok..ok...for those of you who want pics..here you go
Well all right then!
I have pulled a few off of my puppy already this year.Take it any way you want to.They are really bad here this year.Frontline will be needed. Joe
Hey Guys...Beware.... Early tick season this year. Last week, picked one off the dog already!
Thanks for the heads up Julie. I checked last night...not a single tick to be found. Wasn't all for nothing though cause I did find a coupla split shots and car keys that I'd been looking for.
Oh WHAT a stroke of luck!
I am so glad you said beware and not be bebare...
Crap!!! Wish I'd of thought of that!
I can see lots of possibilities for where this thread might go.
..but it's more fun with a friend...
i check myself every morning whether im in the bush or not lol
remember, you can only "check" yourself once or twice before it's called something else.
oh ya..
A guy I used to work with was caught naked with his sister in law by his wife, checking for ticks was his excuse and the wife bought it!!!  gotta love a reasonable country girl
hahah oh man.. gotta stay safe
but did he get his wife to join in???????????? on the chic checking........... oops i mean tick ~~~~~~~~  ~~~~~~~~
i cant believe no one posted this one yet
im going to keep checking back to this thread to see if anyone (female) catches one and actually posts pics...
My wife doesn't have any
relief  i thought i found one in my belly button, it was just a lint ball  maybe hit the dr. office tomoro n let the nurse do a thorough once over, or twice
I need someone to help me check in places I can't see. SWF only need apply
iam sure some of you on here are calling them ticks when they might crabs hahahahahahahahahahahaha
I really did have a good idea this would be a popular subject! All a girl has to do is say "naked" and all hell breaks loose! LOL
Well I tried, and the wife found one tick.  ME!
That must of been a June bug.
You said it!   lol
Personally, I thought that was really generous of you.  I looked around at the smilie selection and I didn't find one of these:
